longBusinessSummary: Digital Asset Monetary Network, Inc. operates as a public accelerator-incubator.  The company funds disruptive and sustainable innovations, solves problems through digital platforms and other electronic applications. The company aligns with other private accelerators and incubators, to form unique partnerships. These partnerships enhance the vetting process, to ensure that the teams, who are developing the cutting edge innovations, are properly funded and acquired. Further, the company partners with entrepreneurs, venture capitalists, and development teams to provide startups with general and functional mentorship. Digital Arts Media Network, Inc. was formerly known as Umairco, Inc. and changed its name to Digital Arts Media Network, Inc. in March 2015. The company is based in Bronx, New York.
